{% extends "layouts/base.njk" %} {% block head %}
<meta property="og:type" content="website" />
{% endblock %} {% block title %}Felipe Moyano | Toughts and Writings{% endblock
%} {% block content %}

<section class="w-full max-w-3xl mx-auto mt-12">
  <div class="px-4 mt-6 content">
    <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 font-display">Felipe Moyano</h2>
    <p>
      I'm Felipe. I' like building products, mostly as a developer, but I've
      been a bit all over the place. I love web development and spent some time
      as a startup founder.
    </p>
    <p>
      Currently I'm an engineering lead at <a href="https://trii.co">trii</a> a
      fintech where we're building the greatest investment platform in LatAm.
      Before that I helped kick-off <a href="https://sumz.co">Sumz</a> a company
      focused on helping one of the largest business group in colombia make the
      most out of their data.
    </p>
    <p>
      Before COVID I was a co-founder at Savy, a consumer app looking to bring
      fitness to everyone by introducing dynamic pricing to fitness and welness
      venues. It was a lot of fun and I learnt a lot.
    </p>
    <p>
      I like to build. Sometime's that means software, othertimes it means teams
      or processes. This is the place where I write about those things.
    </p>
    <p>
      If you'd like to talk to me feel free to reach out via
      <a href="https://x.com/gafemoyano">twitter / X</a> or
      <a href="https://bsky.app/profile/gafemoyano.bsky.social">Bluesky</a>. You can also check what I'm working on at <a href="https://github.com/gafemoyano">Github</a>.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="w-full max-w-3xl mx-auto">
  <div class="px-4 mt-6 py-12">
    <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-10">
      <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 font-display">
        Recent Articles
      </h2>
      <a href="/en/articles" class="hidden sm:inline-flex items-center text-sm font-medium text-lime-700 hover:text-lime-800 transition-colors">
        View all <span class="ml-1">â†’</span>
      </a>
    </div>

    <div class="space-y-8">
      {%- for post in collections.englishPosts | head(-4) | reverse -%}
      <a href="{{ post.url | url }}" class="group block">
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-3 sm:gap-6 items-baseline p-4 -mx-4 rounded-2xl transition-all duration-300 hover:bg-white hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-gray-200/50">
          <div class="sm:w-28 shrink-0 flex items-center gap-3">
            <span class="block w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-gray-300 group-hover:bg-lime-500 transition-colors"></span>
            <time class="text-sm font-mono text-gray-500 group-hover:text-gray-800 transition-colors">
              {{ post.data.date | readableDate }}
            </time>
          </div>

          <div class="flex-1">
            <h3 class="font-display text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 group-hover:text-lime-700 transition-colors mb-2">
              {{ post.data.title }}
            </h3>
            {% if post.data.description %}
              <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed line-clamp-2">
                {{ post.data.description }}
              </p>
            {% endif %}
          </div>
        </div>
      </a>
      {%- endfor -%}
    </div>

    <!-- Mobile Only View All -->
    <div class="mt-8 sm:hidden">
      <a href="/en/articles" class="flex items-center justify-center w-full py-3 text-sm font-medium text-lime-800 bg-lime-50 rounded-lg">
        View all articles
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
{% endblock %}
